### 10. Risks & Mitigations  

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| **GitHub API rate limits** | Medium | Push failures for highâ€‘traffic users | Use GitHub Apps with higher limits; batch pushes via background jobs. |
| **Template stagnation** | Low | Users lose interest if no fresh designs | Open a communityâ€‘driven template marketplace; incentivise contributions with revenue share. |
| **Security of stored OAuth tokens** | High | Compromise leads to repo takeover | Encrypt tokens with Prismaâ€‘compatible `@prisma/client` field encryption; rotate tokens regularly. |
| **Competition from AI generators** | Medium | Users may switch to free AI tools | Offer AIâ€‘assisted template customization as a premium addâ€‘on, not a core free feature. |

